title: #ZekeWatch, How to handle holdouts in fantasy (Football 7/31)
description:
Will Brinson and John Breech break down the latest news and notes around the NFL including Zeke Elliott's holdout and Jerry Jones comments about his RB (2:00), Andrew Luck's calf injury (10:15), Roger Goodell testifying in the Saints-Rams game (12:00) and all kinds of Dolphins shenanigans (15:00). Then Will welcomes on Jamey Eisenberg to break down where he's drafting guys like A.J. Green, Zeke, Melvin Gordon and much more.
